text: Eadward kyning gret Harold eorl & ælfgar eorl & ealle þa ðegnas on Wigeraceastrescire & on Gleaweceastrescire & on Wæringwicscire freondlice.

& ic cyðe eow þæt ic habbe geunnen Wulstane munuce þæt biscoprice into Wihgeraceastre mid sace & mid socne, toll & team, binnan burhge & butan swa full & swa forð swa hit ænig his foregenga fyrmæst on handa stode on eallan þingan.
For þan ic nylle geþafian þæt him ænig mann æt ænigan þingan misbeode oððe him of hande drahge ænig þæra ðinga þe he mid rihte into his biseoprice ahge to habbanne.
